{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323046, "create_time": 1659359691, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "能做大明的狗就是最大的荣幸了，怎么还敢希冀做大明的朋友呢", "timestamp": 1659359691}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323061, "create_time": 1659360023, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "这么划分其实想得太简单。2012之前西方对中国的态度一向大体是友好的，拉中国进世贸，融入全球化建立世界工厂，用经济合作促使中国政治转型一直是西方的主要对华策略，中国也确实是在按着西方的路子走，融入全球化，对外开放和经济发展是主旋律。2012年后某人上台后外交上四处树敌，对内治疆治港政策引发西方质疑，加速一人独裁和军备升级都让西方越来越警惕，这种情况下别说西方了，自己的香港，台湾都人心向背，就连三胖都管不住，周边国家如日韩菲马新外交上越来越远离中国靠近美国，这下自然也就“独裁国家”当朋友了。说白了还是给其他国家的威胁值太高，国际形象太差，外交太失败，内政治理也让人怀疑。与之相比，甚至连朝鲜都觉得美国更加可靠，当时还找川普会谈。这种情况下，说好听点是某人主动孤立全世界，说难听点自然就是被全世界孤立呗。", "timestamp": 1659360023}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323063, "create_time": 1659360066, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "记得朝贡", "timestamp": 1659360066}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323066, "create_time": 1659360220, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "换句话说，12年之前的中国在世界上的形象类似现在的越南，虽然确实是一党专政，也跟民主国家不沾边，但至少还是摆出努力正向改革扩大开放的姿态，再加上本身劳动力市场庞大，因此在西方国家或者其他国家的印象分不至于太差，因此像美国也愿意拉小弟跟现在的越南签自贸协议。12年之前的中国虽然也不是民主国家，但至少还是摆出来很好的姿态和国际形象，奥运会申办成功和2008年大量外国元首万国来朝也是很好的象征。", "timestamp": 1659360220}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323192, "create_time": 1659365857, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 十分同意", "timestamp": 1659365857}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323194, "create_time": 1659365916, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "包帝因为别人写他的小黄文就把香港金融中心干废了，不愧是一代雄主", "timestamp": 1659365916}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323201, "create_time": 1659366070, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 荒谬至极，今天的中国就是八九十年代的日本，经济发展太快被认为可能威胁美国，日本因为进军半导体，中国因为产业升级高新科技。而美国纯粹处于经济发起的贸易战没有达成预期效果，拜登政府又从意识形态着手，重启民主联盟，开始孤立战略。", "timestamp": 1659366070}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323205, "create_time": 1659366327, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Bob: 天真，你以为自己摆出一副无害的姿态别人就不会排斥你吗，苏联解体的时候俄罗斯那么亲西方有什么好结果吗。重返亚太在08年就提出来了，这个时候某人还没上台吧。\n香港的应对可能有异议，但是新疆你有更好的对策吗，是放任恐怖袭击还是放任新疆独立？\n韬光养晦不等于自我阉割，别人西方也不是傻，你想经济发展产业升级迟早会跟别人产生纠纷。", "timestamp": 1659366327}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323208, "create_time": 1659366411, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 放任东突厥斯坦独立", "timestamp": 1659366411}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323209, "create_time": 1659366416, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "所谓香港问题和新疆问题，比起邓小平时期的六四问题，江泽明时期的法轮功问题，孰轻孰重显而易见。这场由贸易战经济战为起点标志的中美对抗，根本原因还是在于经济", "timestamp": 1659366416}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323214, "create_time": 1659366642, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 你换世界上任何一个正常领导人在这个位置都不会放任独立，除非脑子坏掉。", "timestamp": 1659366642}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323216, "create_time": 1659366727, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 爱尔兰是怎么独立的？", "timestamp": 1659366727}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323218, "create_time": 1659366774, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 阿尔及利亚是怎么独立的？", "timestamp": 1659366774}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323220, "create_time": 1659366848, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 战争，新疆有这个能力吗？", "timestamp": 1659366848}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323223, "create_time": 1659366902, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 你不会以为英法是没打仗就同意了吧", "timestamp": 1659366902}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323225, "create_time": 1659366966, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 英法当然有能力建集中营，但没有人会这么做。", "timestamp": 1659366966}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323226, "create_time": 1659367075, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "原来以为翻出墙外的人键政水平会高一点，没想到还有想法这么幼稚的，幻想西方接纳中国和平发展跟粉红幻想皇帝开明有什么区别呢？", "timestamp": 1659367075}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323228, "create_time": 1659367187, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Francis: 你跟这些人说这么多干啥。这种一股脑把锅推到某个人甚至某个决策上的人，本质上跟期待救世主降临的是一类人。", "timestamp": 1659367187}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323229, "create_time": 1659367247, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 想要作为人类被接纳，就要消灭食人者的国家。", "timestamp": 1659367247}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323230, "create_time": 1659367296, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Hans: 第一，不是“某个”；第二，算不上“人”。大概十亿头节肢动物吧。", "timestamp": 1659367296}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323231, "create_time": 1659367398, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Bob: 12年之后的中朝关系明显是越来越好了吧", "timestamp": 1659367398}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323233, "create_time": 1659367453, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 英国怎么对付美洲土著的，英国被消灭了吗。", "timestamp": 1659367453}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323234, "create_time": 1659367478, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Bob: 改革开放以来，朝鲜一直批评中国，而且产生了朝核问题，21世纪初关系是极差的，近几年才变好，好歹学学历史，不要臆想", "timestamp": 1659367478}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323235, "create_time": 1659367484, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 和他们签订协议购买土地。", "timestamp": 1659367484}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323239, "create_time": 1659367620, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 甚至现在美洲白人还在压迫印第安人，美国怎么还不灭亡呢", "timestamp": 1659367620}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323243, "create_time": 1659367671, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 指让印第安人开赌场发财", "timestamp": 1659367671}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323244, "create_time": 1659367677, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 笑死，这句话出来我明白你是什么成分了，继续做你的圣母吧，宝宝", "timestamp": 1659367677}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323246, "create_time": 1659367743, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "西班牙航海家来到美洲大陆，受到了部落酋长的热情接待，然后他们在宴会上绑架了酋长并杀害许多部落居民，索要大量黄金赎金回到欧洲", "timestamp": 1659367743}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323247, "create_time": 1659367796, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 为什么蜘蛛总是喜欢提印第安人啊？你能在不使用网络的前提下说出五个印第安人部落吗？（一点都不难，只要知道“文明五部落”就够了。）你能说出任何三场印第安人是主要参战方的战争吗？", "timestamp": 1659367796}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323249, "create_time": 1659367844, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Eve: 正好，阿兹特克人是食人族。我是不是发过关于食人者的国家的话？", "timestamp": 1659367844}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323264, "create_time": 1659368226, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "虽然确实无法与西方为敌，但实际上不可能、也不能成为朋友。实例可以看非洲国家，开发依赖西方，结果西方跨国公司做了套转让定价出来，资源是拿了，钱却没给。民主和平是好东西，但管不住贪婪的资本家。", "timestamp": 1659368226}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323268, "create_time": 1659368365, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 我替美洲有色人种谢谢您，给了他们一个和平美好的历史。祝您身体健康", "timestamp": 1659368365}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323300, "create_time": 1659369336, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Isabella: 蚌埠 金三18年才首次来中国，之前枪毙他姑父那会中国还在沈阳搞军演，对朝制裁还真认真制裁了那么几年，何谈12年之后越来越好？", "timestamp": 1659369336}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323301, "create_time": 1659369385, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "半个月不上树洞随手一翻就看到个胡扯的，现在树洞流行张口就来吗？", "timestamp": 1659369385}], "create_time": 1659359505, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1659369385, "likenum": 11, "n_attentions": 11, "n_comments": 34, "pid": 91903, "poll": null, "reply": 34, "text": "以发达国家为敌，我们就永远过不上发达国家人民的生活；与专制国家为友，我们就越来越专制。", "timestamp": 1659359505}}